::Feline::

She stayed in the corner.  She looked up at Prowl for the first time 
and nodded to him. She had an uneasy expression on her face.  She 
showed distrust in the male and uncertainty to Iron Raptor.  She 
lowered her head back down.

She said in a very quiet voice,"I'm alright, thank you." She wiped 
her face again with her hand.  She then looked up at the two bots.
In almost a whisper,"What happens now?"  

She still had her arms wrapped agound her, her tail was still just 
hanging there, not moving like normal.  She showed all signes of 
tension, uneasiness, uncertainty and some distrust.  She had been 
with the Maximals that long them to trust her. Or her to trust them 
yet.
